components.name: PaymentsTableComponent
components.templateData:
<ngx-datatable
    class="table"
    [rows]="payments"
    columnMode="force"
    [headerHeight]="50"
    [rowHeight]="'auto'"
    (sort)="onSort($event)"
    [limit]="pageSize"
    [offset]="pageNumber - 1"
    [messages]="{emptyMessage: 'Sem pagamentos...'}"
>
    <ngx-datatable-column prop="user.name" name="Usu√°rio">
        <ng-template let-value="value" let-row="row" ngx-datatable-cell-template>
            <app-user-info [user]="row.user"></app-user-info>
        </ng-template>
    </ngx-datatable-column>
    <ngx-datatable-column prop="user.title" name="T√≠tulo">
        <ng-template let-value="value" ngx-datatable-cell-template>
            {{value}}
        </ng-template>
    </ngx-datatable-column>
    <ngx-datatable-column prop="date" name="Data">
        <ng-template let-value="value" ngx-datatable-cell-template>
            <app-date-info [date]="value"></app-date-info>
        </ng-template>
    </ngx-datatable-column>
    <ngx-datatable-column prop="value" name="Valor">
        <ng-template let-value="value" ngx-datatable-cell-template>
            {{value | currency:'BRL'}}
        </ng-template>
    </ngx-datatable-column>
    <ngx-datatable-column prop="status" name="Pago">
        <ng-template let-value="value" let-row="row"  ngx-datatable-cell-template>
            <mat-checkbox [checked]="value"  color="primary" (change)="toggleStatus($event, row.uuid)"></mat-checkbox>
        </ng-template>
    </ngx-datatable-column>
    <ngx-datatable-column prop="" name="">
        <ng-template let-value="value" class="action-cell" ngx-datatable-cell-template>
            <mat-icon>edit</mat-icon>
            <mat-icon>highlight_off</mat-icon>
        </ng-template>
    </ngx-datatable-column>
</ngx-datatable>
